 list. This query can be expressed either with a simple query language or with flags.\n\n```\ngit-bug ls [\u003cquery\u003e] [flags]\n```\n\n### Examples\n\n```\nList open bugs sorted by last edition with a query:\ngit bug ls \"status:open sort:edit-desc\"\n\nList closed bugs sorted by creation with flags:\ngit bug ls --status closed --by creation\n\n```\n\n### Options\n\n```\n  -s, --status strings     Filter by status. Valid values are [open,closed]\n  -a, --author strings     Filter by author\n  -l, --label strings      Filter by label\n  -n, --no strings         Filter by absence of something. Valid values are [label]\n  -b, --by string          Sort the results by a characteristic. Valid values are [id,creation,edit] (default \"creation\")\n  -d, --direction string   Select the sorting direction. Valid values are [asc,desc] (default \"asc\")\n  -h, --help               help for ls\n```","files":null},{"type":3,"timestamp":1536596580,"metadata":{"github-id":"MDEyOklzc3VlQ29tbWVudDQxOTk3MzYwOA==","github-url":"https://github.com/MichaelMure/git-bug/issues/21#issuecomment-419973608"},"nonce":"A8Kcv0PDOHyQnPR5LahxumUlbGk=","message":"Only things left:\n\n- graphql api\n- termui integration","files":null},{"type":3,"timestamp":1536688433,"metadata":{"github-id":"MDEyOklzc3VlQ29tbWVudDQyMDM2MjY3OA==","github-url":"https://github.com/MichaelMure/git-bug/issues/21#issuecomment-420362678"},"nonce":"kP8sDWgbuqpf9TSmRAaf6pBFaLw=","message":"And those are done as well ! That was a journey in itself ...","files":null},{"type":4,"timestamp":1536688563,"metadata":{"github-id":"MDExOkNsb3NlZEV2ZW50MTgzOTE5NzM3Mg=="},"nonce":"l2Smy+Kl5AjZq0+raI+XtlXrcZw=","status":2}]}